{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to &quot;The Darkened Halls&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock the Secrets, Defeat the Darkness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare to immerse yourself in a world of chilling secrets where darkness is not the only adversary you'll face. <i>&quot;The Darkened Halls&quot;</i> is a psychological horror game that pushes the boundaries of fear, challenging you with secrets to uncover and formidable bosses to defeat using wit and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>See the Game In Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/extras/The_Darkened_Halls_Blood_Cave.gif?t=1737421182\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/extras/The_Darkened_Halls_Jumping_Section_Steam.gif?t=1737421182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/extras/The_Darkened_Halls_Puzzle_Solving_Steam.gif?t=1737421182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/extras/The_Darkened_Halls_Boss_Chase_Steam.gif?t=1737421182\" />Witness the heart-pounding moment when Clara is pursued by a fearsome boss, requiring swift thinking to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay At A Glance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>&quot;The Darkened Halls&quot;</i> offers a unique horror experience, focusing on strategy and puzzle-solving rather than combat. Dive into gameplay that:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> **Relies on Wits, Not Weapons:** Meet Clara, a young girl who defies conventions. She's resourceful, agile, and exceptionally intelligent. Clara's sharp mind is your greatest asset.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> **Face Your Fears:** Navigate a world where darkness reigns, and unimaginable horrors lurk. Outsmart the terrors in a game that challenges your ability to think strategically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> **Uncover Secrets:** Behind the chilling atmosphere lies a web of enigmas. Clara's journey will test your problem-solving skills as you decipher cryptic puzzles and unlock hidden truths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> **Conquer Formidable Bosses:** <i>&quot;The Darkened Halls&quot;</i> isn't for the faint-hearted. Multiple formidable bosses await, and they can't be defeated with brute force. Tactical thinking, wit, and cunning are your greatest weapons.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Are You Ready?</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Venture into the Unknown</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're seeking an immersive psychological horror experience that challenges your intellect and tactical prowess, <i>&quot;The Darkened Halls&quot;</i> is the ultimate destination. Dive headfirst into the abyss, confront your fears, and join Clara on a journey that demands both courage and strategy.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737421182","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737421182","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737421182","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2565460/capsule_184x69.jpg